profile:
No matter what your project is, you need a contractor you can trust! 

At TSC Homes we commit to creating a courteous work environment in your home and in your neighbourhood.  
Our team has a reputation of being hard working and friendly. We believe in open communication with our clients.

You can rely on us to see your project through from concept to completion. You will have piece of mind knowing that your project is in our hands. Join our growing list of clients who know that we deliver on our promises, in every way!

Allow TSC Homes (Top Standard Contracting) the opportunity to show you what makes us different. 

Schedule a one-on-one consultation with our Project Manager today. 

-------------------

More about JOSH GARYFALAKIS
Owner/Project Manager
​
Josh started his construction career as a framer. From there he went to work in a cabinet makers' shop. It was at the shop where his appreciation for fine finishings and quality custom work grew. In Hamilton, ON, Josh worked as the Project Manager for multiple commercial builds. He gained experience in hiring, managing and scheduling multiple trades across multiple projects. 
​
Clients across Burlington, Oakville, Dundas and Hamilton have trusted Josh with their projects. They know that he brings his expert knowledge, passion for excellence and outstanding work ethic to everything he does. 

Whether you are ready to build your dream home or want to transform your current house, we’re the right Custom Home Builder for you. 
We are ready to walk you through each phase of your project and are dedicated to making your visions a reality.
